      <body>
         <head type="date">
            <date when="1804-12-28">December 28, 1804</date>
         </head>
         <div type="entry" xml:id="lc.jrn.1804-12-28.01" n="lc.geo.1804-12-28.01">
            <sp who="wc">
               <speaker>
                  <name type="person" key="Clark, William">Clark</name>
                  <ref target="n09122801" n="1"/>
               </speaker>
               <ab>
                  <date>28th of <hi rend="italic">December Friday 1804</hi>
                  </date>
               </ab>
               <p>
blew verry hard last night, the frost fell like a Shower of Snow, nothing remarkable to day, the Snow Drifting from one bottom to another and from the leavel plains into the hollows &amp;c 

</p>
            </sp>
         </div>
         <div type="entry" xml:id="lc.jrn.1804-12-28.02" n="lc.geo.1804-12-28.01">
            <sp who="jo">
               <speaker>Ordway</speaker>
               <ab>
                  <date/>
               </ab>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Friday 28th Decr</hi>.    clear &amp; cold.    high wind    Some of the Savages visited us.—

</p>
            </sp>
         </div>
      </body>
